    "body": "Suggestion: to determine if build is up-to-date:\r\n- create a list of configuration files, source, and output folders.\r\n- hash all files (including recursively all current files in source, dest)\r\n- put this hash in output folder\r\n- whenever rebuilding, perform the above hash again - and verify it matches previous hash.\r\n- any change to source (or ouputs) will cause rebuild..",
